#. Section heading (H2)
msgctxt "intro.h2"
msgid "What to Look for in Appointment Scheduling Software"
msgstr ""

#. Intro paragraph 1
msgctxt "intro.p1"
msgid "The appointment scheduling market has never been more crowded. Calendly dominates meeting-scheduling for sales teams. Acuity Scheduling is a long-standing choice for service businesses. Setmore appeals to solo operators with its generous free plan. SimplyBook.me offers the most feature-complete option for service businesses - with 40+ payment gateways, HIPAA compliance from the Standard plan, a built-in loyalty program, and a branded client app."
msgstr ""

#. Intro paragraph 2 (list lead-in)
msgctxt "intro.p2"
msgid "Before choosing a platform, most service businesses ask these five questions:"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — checklist item 1
msgctxt "intro.list.item1"
msgid "Does it have a free plan, or will I be paying from day one?"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — checklist item 2
msgctxt "intro.list.item2"
msgid "Can it accept payments from clients in my country?"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — checklist item 3
msgctxt "intro.list.item3"
msgid "Does it meet my industry's compliance requirements (HIPAA, GDPR)?"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — checklist item 4
msgctxt "intro.list.item4"
msgid "What happens to my bill when my team grows?"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — checklist item 5
msgctxt "intro.list.item5"
msgid "Does it offer revenue-generating features like memberships, packages, and gift cards?"
msgstr ""

#. Intro — CTA button
msgctxt "intro.cta"
msgid "Try SimplyBook.me Free"
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 1 — heading
msgctxt "intro.highlight1.h3"
msgid "40+ Payment Gateways"
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 1 — body
msgctxt "intro.highlight1.p"
msgid "Stripe, PayPal, Mollie, Adyen, Worldpay, Alipay, CCAvenue, and dozens of regional processors. Accept bookings from clients anywhere in the world."
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 2 — heading
msgctxt "intro.highlight2.h3"
msgid "HIPAA from Standard Plan"
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 2 — body
msgctxt "intro.highlight2.p"
msgid "HIPAA BAA capability at €24.90/month annually - not locked behind the most expensive tier. ISO 27001 certified (recertified 2024)."
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 3 — heading
msgctxt "intro.highlight3.h3"
msgid "Built-in Loyalty Program"
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 3 — body
msgctxt "intro.highlight3.p"
msgid "Points-based rewards system, memberships, multi-session packages, and gift cards - all included on paid plans to help you grow revenue."
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 4 — heading
msgctxt "intro.highlight4.h3"
msgid "Branded Client App"
msgstr ""

#. Highlight card 4 — body
